name: Reflect
description:
No I this is not a painting. I don't know how to. But I should've learned when I had the chance. Only if there was a way to download painting skills. Like in The Matrix. That would be cool. But only for that moment though. Cuz the mind would wonder out to what else that can be copied. What other "false" that excites me or my ego. Clout? Wealth? Freedom? Peace? Isolation? Beauty? Friendship? A fuking job? Which one really?


"Scrollin' through Pornhub, I'm on page 50" - Lil Boom
